{"tid":1365872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果星期六元朗自製戒嚴 ...","createTime":"2019-07-25T19:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T19:28:17.000Z","uid":264819,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"296d9600404c03057af1a35284133077c2ec6e80","tid":1365872,"uid":264819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"我哋去嘅目的係鳩烏，食好西，買老婆餅，咁先可以反白色恐怖，反警黑合作，爭取返市民免於恐懼嘅自由<br />\n<br />\n無論尖沙咀定係多次港島遊行，都唔會有鋪頭一早落晒閘，好多仲係好歡迎我哋。如果元朗商戶一早落晒閘，唔歡迎我哋去幫襯，其實我哋可以考慮下突然決定唔去，然後個個星期六日用同一路線申請遊行，睇下佢哋頂得幾耐。連一樓一都冇人去，我唔信日日自製戒嚴嘅話，啲牛屎佬黑幫喺元朗咁多生意頂得住好耐。講到尾，黑社會幾愛共國都好，都係要開飯"},{"pid":"13f83c7f64c6a24a03a771ab9105a8d25d1d79ea","tid":1365872,"uid":264819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf4969974959d870fdc77504bffe6294d6390dd","tid":1365872,"uid":264819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48195202ce2ac255bdb2b2ee7b92cb558070ef7a","tid":1365872,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:14:31.000Z","msg":"古惑仔唔洗食飯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個星期都申請 直至比行為止"},{"pid":"583d220f6f6de26b87d9cd6d3ef2deb80d2b70fa","tid":1365872,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"無生意點交保護費，咁又點收保險費<br />\n你咪唔好開，睇你定我頂得耐啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB仔就免啦，食711都唔食佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c8d80d0c0fa19d31290298546c51b1b9e8ea20","tid":1365872,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:26:53.000Z","msg":"組一團超級大團嘅旅遊團有無得搞"},{"pid":"37b2ba98a369a2c44e03e9fd4fa9fa95b3c6f30c","tid":1365872,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<br />\n而且行街咁簡單，和理非都可以去，隨時愈來愈多人。"}]}